                <div class="sc-faq wow fadeInLeft animated" data-wow-delay="0.3ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms">
                    <div class="inner-faq">
                        <h4 class="title clr-pri-2">Cancellation & Refund Policy</h4>
                        <p class="f-mulish clr-pri-4">Aromat believes in helping parents as far as possible, and has therefore a liberal cancellation policy.</p>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h5 class="faq-question"><i class="fas fa-check-circle clr-pri-3"></i> How do I cancel my order?</h5>
                            <p class="f-mulish clr-pri-4">Cancellations can be considered only if the request is made immediately after placing the order. However, the cancellation request may not be entertained if the orders have been communicated to the vendors and they have initiated the shipping process. If so, you can always reach out to us.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h5 class="faq-question"><i class="fas fa-check-circle clr-pri-3"></i> What if I receive damaged items?</h5>
                            <p class="f-mulish clr-pri-4">In case of receipt of damaged or defective items please report the same to our Customer Service team within 2 days of receipt. The request will be entertained once the merchant has checked and determined the same.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h5 class="faq-question"><i class="fas fa-check-circle clr-pri-3"></i> Product not as expected?</h5>
                            <p class="f-mulish clr-pri-4">If you feel that the product received is not as shown on the site or as per your expectations, you must bring it to our notice within 2 days of receiving the product.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="sc-faq wow fadeInRight animated" data-wow-delay="0.5ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms">
                    <div class="inner-faq">
                        <h4 class="title clr-pri-2">Shipping Policy</h4>
                        <p class="f-mulish clr-pri-4">We make sure your order reaches you safely and on time.</p>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h5 class="faq-question"><i class="fas fa-truck clr-pri-3"></i> How are orders shipped?</h5>
                            <p class="f-mulish clr-pri-4">For Sri Lankan parents, orders are shipped through registered domestic courier companies and/or speed post only.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h5 class="faq-question"><i class="fas fa-clock clr-pri-3"></i> Delivery time</h5>
                            <p class="f-mulish clr-pri-4">Orders are shipped within 3-5 days or as per the delivery date agreed at the time of order confirmation, subject to Courier Company / post office norms.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h5 class="faq-question"><i class="fas fa-headset clr-pri-3"></i> Need help?</h5>
